\pard\pardeftab720\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 The concept of a "view" on YouTube is not a static definition; it represents a dynamically evaluated metric subject to rigorous algorithmic validation to strip out bot traffic and inorganic inflation.\

